s=3D"sl-markdown-content"> <p>Use the Netlify REST API to manage atomic dep=
loys of your sites and apps, manage form submissions, inject JavaScript sni=
ppets, manage DNS, and so much more.</p>
<div class=3D"video-container astro-7qzxku2k"> <iframe width=3D"560" height=
=3D"315" src=3D"cid:frame-C7532442477CC546900AC825D6C60471@mhtml.blink" tit=
le=3D"YouTube video player" loading=3D"lazy" allow=3D"accelerometer; autopl=
ay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-sh=
are" allowfullscreen=3D"" class=3D"astro-7qzxku2k"></iframe> </div>
<p>This document covers the basics for interacting with the Netlify API, pl=
us instructions for <a href=3D"https://docs.netlify.com/api-and-cli-guides/=
api-guides/get-started-with-api#deploy-with-the-api">deploying sites</a> an=
d notes on some <a href=3D"https://docs.netlify.com/api-and-cli-guides/api-=
guides/get-started-with-api#commonly-used-endpoints">commonly used endpoint=
s</a>.</p>
<p>You can browse the <a href=3D"https://open-api.netlify.com/" class=3D"ex=
ternal-link" rel=3D"noopener noreferrer" target=3D"_blank">OpenAPI referenc=
e for the Netlify API</a> to explore available endpoints. Visit our Forums =
for more tips and conversation about <a href=3D"https://answers.netlify.com=
/t/common-issue-understanding-and-using-netlifys-api/160" class=3D"external=
-link" rel=3D"noopener noreferrer" target=3D"_blank">understanding and usin=
g Netlify=E2=80=99s API</a>.</p>
<p>Additionally, we have two API clients for your convenience:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href=3D"https://github.com/netlify/open-api#go-client" class=3D"exte=
rnal-link" rel=3D"noopener noreferrer" target=3D"_blank">Go Client</a></li>
<li><a href=3D"https://github.com/netlify/build/tree/main/packages/js-clien=
t" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"noopener noreferrer" target=3D"_blank">JS=
 Client</a></li>
</ul>
<p>If you=E2=80=99d like to interact with the Netlify API using a no-code t=
ool, you can use n8n.io=E2=80=99s <a href=3D"https://n8n.io/integrations/ne=
tlify/" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"noopener noreferrer" target=3D"_blan=
k">Netlify node</a>. The node currently supports the following operations:<=
/p>
<ul>
<li>Create a new deployment</li>
<li>Get a deployment</li>
<li>Get all deployments</li>
<li>Cancel a deployment</li>
<li>Get a site</li>
<li>Get all sites</li>
<li>Delete a site</li>
</ul>
