=9D</span></a></div>
<p>All API requests that return over 100 items are paginated by default, wi=
th a limit of 100 items per page. You can specify further pages with the <c=
ode dir=3D"auto">?page</code> parameter. You can also set a custom page siz=
e that=E2=80=99s less than 100 with the <code dir=3D"auto">?per_page</code>=
 parameter.</p>
<p>Note that page numbering starts with 1 and that omitting the <code dir=
=3D"auto">?page</code> parameter will return the first page.</p>
