<p><code dir=3D"auto">PATCH /api/v1/sites/{site_id}</code> updates some att=
ributes on a site.</p>
<p><code dir=3D"auto">PUT /api/v1/sites/{site_id}</code> updates some attri=
butes on a site.</p>
<p>This lets you update a site. It takes all the same parameters as when cr=
eating a site.</p>
<p>If you do a PUT request to a site with <code dir=3D"auto">Content-Type: =
application/zip</code> and a zipped website in the HTTP request body, it wo=
rks exactly like creating a new deploy for the site based on a ZIP file.</p=
>
