<p><code dir=3D"auto">POST /api/v1/sites/{site_id}/ssl</code> activates SSL=
 for a site.</p>
<p>The site must have a custom domain with DNS records configured to point =
to Netlify=E2=80=99s infrastructure.</p>
<p>Any domain aliases with valid DNS records will also be included in the S=
SL certificate for the site.</p>
<p>This endpoint manually triggers SSL provisioning for a site=E2=80=99s cu=
stom domains. Once SSL provisioning is successful, the domain will be serve=
d over HTTPS.</p>
