<p><code dir=3D"auto">PUT /api/v1/accounts/{account_id}/env/{key}</code> up=
dates an existing environment variable by replacing all of its values with =
the values provided with this request.</p>
<p><code dir=3D"auto">PATCH /api/v1/accounts/{account_id}/env/{key}</code> =
updates or creates a new value for an existing environment variable.</p>
