<p><code dir=3D"auto">GET /api/v1/sites/{site_id}/submissions?state=3Dspam<=
/code> returns a list of spam form submissions across all forms for a speci=
fic site.</p>
<p><code dir=3D"auto">GET /api/v1/forms/{form_id}/submissions?state=3Dspam<=
/code> returns a list of spam form submissions for a specific form.</p>
